{
  "id": "adv_event_2110_01_03",
  "title": "強い想い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-03.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.2333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにも……いないよな\n……ははっ、何やってんだ俺は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s not here… as well.\n*sigh* What am I doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1,
      "endTime": 10.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もう麻奈はいないんだ。そんなことは分かってる\n……それでも、やっぱり寂しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana’s gone. I know that.\n…But I just still miss her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 22.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　校門の所に誰か立ってる……\nあれは……さくら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? There’s someone standing at the school gate…\nIs that… Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 31.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "よかったです\n{user}さんが見つかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad‚\nI found you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.333333333333336,
      "endTime": 36.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "心配掛けてすまなかった\nまさかスマホの充電が切れてるなんて思わなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for worrying you.\nI had no idea my phone was out of charge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 42.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、少し歩かないかって提案してくれて助かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And your suggestion of going for a walk was a big help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1,
      "endTime": 48.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、それならよかったです\n……落ち着く時間が必要かなって思ったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I’m glad I could help.\n…I thought maybe you needed some time to relax.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9,
      "endTime": 55.59562505086263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……\nどうして俺が学校にいるって分かったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at you‚ though.\nHow did you know I’d be at the school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8,
      "endTime": 60.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんが、あの場所に呼んでくれた気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a feeling that Mana-san took me there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "endTime": 64.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈が……？　でも、もうさくらの心臓は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana did…? But your heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 69.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。麻奈さんがいなくなって以来\n心臓が私に教えてくれることはなくなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Since Mana-san disappeared‚\nmy heart hasn’t had anything else to tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 76.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なぜか今日だけは……\n麻奈さんが、教えてくれた気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But for some reason‚ just today…\nI get the feeling Mana-san is telling me something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1,
      "endTime": 83.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことって……あるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that even… possible?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 87.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "分かりません\nあれ以来、初めてのことですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.\nIt’s the first time it’s happened since…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 92.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも……今日は、麻奈さんが本当の意味で\nいなくなってから、初めての誕生日ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But today is Mana-san’s first birthday\nsince she is real gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 100.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "きっと奇跡の一つくらい\n起こっても不思議じゃないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wouldn’t be so strange if\nthe miracle happened again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "endTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが\n一人ぼっちで悲しまないように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe she led me here‚ {user}-san‚\nso you wouldn’t be here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9,
      "endTime": 110.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "って、導いてくれたのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "alone and lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 113.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか。奇跡、か\n……俺、つい昨日まで、麻奈の誕生日を忘れてたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. A miracle‚ huh?\nYou know‚ I forgot all about Mana’s birthday until yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 125.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなをトップアイドルにしようと必死で走るうちに\n麻奈への想いを疎かにしてたのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While I’ve been scurrying around trying to make you all into top idols‚\nI was neglecting to think about Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "endTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺は……本当に酷い奴だよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I’m a terrible person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.63333333333333,
      "endTime": 137.6333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 140.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんへの強い想いがあったからこそ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it’s because you had such strong feelings",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3,
      "endTime": 143.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\n走り続けてきたんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ {user}-san\nwere able to go on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 148.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、麻奈さんの誕生日なら、これから毎年\n星見プロのみんなでお祝いすればいいんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I think it’d be good if we celebrated Mana-san’s birthday\nat Hoshimi Productions every year from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.36666666666667,
      "endTime": 155.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だな\nさくら、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you’re right.\nSakura… Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.26666666666668,
      "endTime": 162.73333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.26666666666668,
      "endTime": 165.50000000000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、電話です\nちょっと待ってて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ a phone call.\nWait a minute‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7,
      "endTime": 169.60000000000002,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし？　さくら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello? Sakura?",
